title: Contemporary African Arts and Crafts (Art Ebook).pdf
description:
Crown | 1974 | Pdf | Eng | 306 pages | 43.4 MB

Designed for all who admire the magnificent, richly decorative art of Africa, this new book will allow both novice and advanced craftsmen to turn out breathtakingly beautiful objects derived from the art of ancient as well as present-day Africa. Thoroughly researched by Thelma Newman, who traveled extensively throughout Africa, this excellent volume is profusely illustrated with on-the-spot photographs showing the step by step methods of the native artisans
